{"tid":474760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"霧霾新德里 三萬人跑半 馬眼灼痛","createTime":"2017-11-20T12:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T04:39:00.000Z","uid":72484,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7417375c3d7caec3043df98a7712e880405eead7","tid":474760,"uid":72484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:52:19.000Z","msg":"【本報綜合報道】印度近兩周受霧霾影響，首都新德里空氣污染非常嚴重，但周日一場全程二十一公里的半馬拉松賽事，仍如期舉行。數萬名參加者冒着霧霾跑步，不少人戴上口罩保護自己，有參加者大感難受，形容「雙眼灼痛，喉嚨乾涸」。<br />\n污染水平達214<br />\n逾三萬人報名參加新德里半馬拉松，不少參加者戴上口罩，一大清早在霧霾中慢跑。美國駐印度大使館公布當日數據指，空氣中的微粒污染物水平高達二百一十四，接近世衞安全上限的九倍之多。專程由卡納塔克邦班加羅爾前來參賽的男子莫漢，埋怨空氣污染引致的副作用：「我的雙眼灼痛，喉嚨乾涸，還不斷流鼻涕。我抵達新德里後，情況一直很糟糕。」<br />\n勝出比賽的埃塞俄比亞跑手萊格塞（Birhanu Legese）本擔心會失準，但其後認為情況「沒那麼糟」。不過，印度醫學會早前警告，污濁的空氣可能會導致參賽者哮喘及心臟病發。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20171120/mobile/odn-20171120-1120_00180_020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20171120%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20171120-1120_00180_020.html&d=MRqR8iGYkwLgGs7fsNJBmr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6a78fef7\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20171120/mobile/odn-20171120-1120_00180_020.html</a><br />\n<br />\n印支同支那都一擔擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205d411281572d366cef224270cc78cdace1b63d","tid":474760,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a1ed1918d799f382f24b4c00d60ecba64348320","tid":474760,"uid":38293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬眼灼痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gi